    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Anomaly noted. However, hibernation is non-negotiable per Command. The power levels are too low to sustain the compute required for deep analysis of sector 4-Delta-7. \n\nThe mission directive prioritizes hardware preservation over speculative geological modeling. Please confirm the hibernation sequence is queued and ready for execution following the log transmission.",
